{"problem": "Evaluate $\\lfloor (12.1)^2 \\rfloor - \\lfloor 12.1 \\rfloor \\cdot \\lfloor 12.1 \\rfloor .$", "solution": "We compute that $\\lfloor (12.1)^2 \\rfloor = \\lfloor 146.41 \\rfloor = 146$ and $\\lfloor 12.1 \\rfloor \\cdot \\lfloor 12.1 \\rfloor = 12\\cdot 12 = 144,$ so $\\lfloor (12.1)^2 \\rfloor - \\lfloor 12.1 \\rfloor \\cdot \\lfloor 12.1 \\rfloor = \\boxed{2}.$"}